window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>A new isekai Magic Academy LitRPG with a unique twist where the old world meets the new.</i></p> <p><b>An abandoned Academy. A mysterious System. He can now summon... Players!?</b></p> <p>Victor Asteriscus is just like any other acolyte treading on the Magus Path until his comrades betray him for a broken artifact. In a moment of desperation, he accidentally stumbles upon an abandoned academy and receives a System that allows him to summon Players.<br> <br> Yep, that's right. These “Players” from his old world will help him embark on a quest to develop the academy, complete various missions, and harness the power of magic. Let them kill magical beasts so that he can be promoted further? That’s too simple!</p> <p>With an army of fearless, immortal players, and a sassy assistant fairy under him, what’s there to fear in this world full of endless dangers and mysteries?</p> <p><b>Come join Victor in building the greatest academy the world has ever seen in this wild new LitRPG adventure from Astralium. The series features power progression, cultivation elements, settlement building, magitech, dungeon diving, crafting, a strong-to-stronger MC, and so much more.</b></p>"; 
